text: Mairelis Zunzunegui (born 8 July 1986) is a Cuban water polo player. She was a member of the Cuba women's national water polo team at the 2019 Pan American Games and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== ==Other websites== *Swim Swam profile * cuban-goalkeeper-mairelis-zunzunegui-tries-to-catch *cuban-goalkeeper-mairelis-zunzunegui-stops-a-ball- Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban water polo players
